name: MultipleFaceDice
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: multiple face dice
des:
Multiple Face Dice is a dice of multiple faces.
You can set the number of faces freely. 

Select number of faces and roll the dice (for example. 10 faces): 10, 10 faces, 10 Please
Roll the dice again with the previous number of faces: roll the dice again, roll again, again, next
